\f2\i very
\f1\i0 \'a0little bit. Ours are all apple-tarts. You need not be afraid of unwholesome preserves here. I do not advise the custard. Mrs. Goddard, what say you to\'a0
\f2\i half
\f1\i0 \'a0a glass of wine? A\'a0
